\fs32 BBCut and other libraries: \

\fs24 \
This extension library for SC3 doesn't overwrite any common classes, so I hope you'll have no problems installing it alongside other third party libraries. There might be a few problems with name clashes of classes, but I have avoided obvious names like Cut, Cutter etc. \
